Gazette  Notice  No.  5971  of  2024,  published  the  water  and  sanitation  tariffs  for  Gatanga  Water  and  Sanitation  Company (GATAWASCO);

And whereas, upon further review and consideration of Murang'a County Government subsidy to GATAWASCO, it has been determined that the tariffs need to be revised downwards;

Now, therefore, pursuant to section 72 (1) (b) and (2) of the Water Act 2016, the Water Services Regulatory Board revokes the tariff structure published in the

Gazette Notice No. 5970 of 2024, published the water and sanitation tariffs for Gatamathi Water and Sanitation Company;

And whereas, upon further review and consideration of Murang'a County Government subsidy to Gatamathi Water and Sanitation Company, it has been determined that the tariffs need to be revised downwards;

Now, therefore, pursuant to section 72 (1) (b) and (2) of the Water Act 2016, the Water Services Regulatory Board revokes the tariff structure published in the

Gazette Notice No. 5964, dated 17th May 2024, published the water and sanitation tariffs for Murang'a West Water and Sanitation Company (MWEWASCO);

